    <narrativeNotes>Angrboda, or Angra to her colleges, was a mighty Jotun and one of the rarely seen Jotun saviours of the rim, who dedicate their lives to combating threats and relishing battle. An experimental weapon was deployed against her and she awoke in the backrooms, where she was discovered by Grignr. Eventually the two married, and Grignr taught Angra his chi-cultivation philosophy. The two became an unstoppable duo.</narrativeNotes>
